---
---

<section id="servicios" class="section relative">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-5">Cómo publicamos tu sitio</div>
      <h2 class="heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight">
        Empieza con <span class="text-brand-yellow">subdominio gratis</span>,
        crece con tu <span class="text-brand-blue">dominio propio</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">
        Te damos flexibilidad total: puedes lanzar hoy sin gastar en dominio, o traer el tuyo
        cuando estés listo. Nosotros nos encargamos de conectarlo por ti.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="relative card card-hover p-8 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-16 -right-16 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow/10 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="h-11 w-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-yellow/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4B400" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-yellow">Opción 1</span>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-display font-black text-2xl text-white">Subdominio gratis</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">
            Publicamos tu sitio en un subdominio nuestro, listo para compartir.
            <strong class="text-white"> Sin costo adicional</strong>.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-brand-bg/60 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-sm">
            <span class="text-brand-muted">https://</span>
            <span class="text-brand-yellow font-semibold">tunegocio</span>
            <span class="text-white">.programmasters.net</span>
          </div>

          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4B400" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-brand-muted">Perfecto para empezar sin inversión inicial</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4B400" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-brand-muted">HTTPS y hosting incluidos</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F4B400" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-brand-muted">Puedes migrar a tu propio dominio cuando quieras</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative card card-hover p-8 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-16 -right-16 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-brand-blue/15 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="h-11 w-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1E63D6" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15 15 0 010 20M12 2a15 15 0 000 20"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-blue">Opción 2</span>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-display font-black text-2xl text-white">Dominio propio</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">
            Usamos el dominio que ya tienes, o compramos uno nuevo para ti. Cero configuración
            técnica de tu lado.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-brand-bg/60 px-4 py-3 font-mono text-sm">
            <span class="text-brand-muted">https://</span>
            <span class="text-white">www.</span>
            <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">tunegocio</span>
            <span class="text-white">.com</span>
          </div>

          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1E63D6" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-brand-muted">Más credibilidad frente a tus clientes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1E63D6" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-brand-muted">Incluido gratis en el Plan Corporativo</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1E63D6" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-brand-muted">Configuramos DNS, correo y HTTPS por ti</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
